datasets.name: Latest 48 Hours Of Solar Wind Data from the SOHO Spacecraft
datasets.description: The latest 48 hours of solar wind data (snapshot) brought to you by the CELIAS/MTOF Proton Monitor on the SOHO Spacecraft.  Data ending at 1553 GMT on Aug 31, 2009 Modified for this dataset. Some Descriptive Text: http://umtof.umd.edu/pm/whatplot.html Real-Time ASCII Data Source: http://umtof.umd.edu/pm/pmsw.used
